{"tid":2011732,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴之戰】撕連儂牆文宣 推倒途人致骨折 自閉青年判囚14天","createTime":"2020-05-11T08:01:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T19:01:12.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4122a42b09a4606ace7e1ae687a8872a55c7b130","tid":2011732,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T08:01:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200511/NWJ7GMEZUQLEY5JAPX2JKKYCXU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200511%2FNWJ7GMEZUQLEY5JAPX2JKKYCXU%2F&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=5d08f49d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200511%2FNWJ7GMEZUQLEY5JAPX2JKKYCXU%2F&h=2cd6ba47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200511/NWJ7GMEZUQLEY5JAPX2JKKYCXU/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年721元朗恐襲翌日，患有自閉症的青年到北角撕毀連儂牆文宣，並襲擊兩名制止他的途人，令其中一人盆骨骨折。青年早前承認兩項襲擊傷人罪，裁判官林希維今判刑時指，考慮到被告心理狀況及事主傷勢等因素，認為不適合判處社會服務令，終判被告監禁14天。林官叮囑被告及早處理情緒問題，又指其母在案發後曾向機構求助，幫助兒子改善社交技巧，故即使昨天兩母子不能慶祝母親節，亦希望被告出獄後能向母親道謝。"},{"pid":"37104b8b27981dde3fedfff23f4050fda9a05003","tid":2011732,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T08:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2KSoh39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2KSoh39.png&h=30a15340&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b8a4d90d8d259fc2912b3a7ec6aa1ed22b25eea","tid":2011732,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T08:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cfUkZDw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcfUkZDw.gif&h=3e367a82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63d2901556047e6378206ea721239f291c1c2973","tid":2011732,"uid":107577,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2b8a4d90d8d259fc2912b3a7ec6aa1ed22b25eea","tid":2011732,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":7,"scor